HEADWORD: Shea tree
<hw>She"a tree`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An African
sapotaceous tree (<spn>Bassia Parkii</spn> syn. <spn>Butyrospermum
Parkii</spn>), from the seeds of which a substance resembling butter is
obtained; the African butter tree.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

